<p>英 /ˌsepə'reɪʃn/    美 /ˌsepə'reɪʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 分离；分开：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This unjust separation of people on the basis of skin color was challenged.
这种基于肤色的不公正种族隔离政策受到了质疑。</p><footer>人教⑩ – 3</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Separation from</strong> his family made him very sad.
与家人分开使他非常伤心。</p></div>

